											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player rages against the vines to snap them and succeeds. In response Jaheira reels back but then returns to a spell-casting pose, ready to kill the player - she still beleives them to be a True Soul. &#xD;&#xA;[greg reshoot] have her start casting Flaming Sphere between first and second line; more threatening please" />
